 />\n中原係血統大雜燴<br />\n中原人都有胡人血統<br />\n所以自唐開始大家都係一家人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e09f8f622963de0316efff29c1059d4de5cf78","tid":913112,"uid":169254,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:46:19.000Z","msg":"其實係咪宋朝遺裔有咩重要<br />\n清朝統治者係滿洲人 文化係滿洲文化 理撚得佢邊到嚟?<br />\n咁講嘅話成個地球都係非洲皇族<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n垃圾人種又想打飛機證明自己冇俾外人統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1337022e7c165401544a504aa28c1d7fe102fa42","tid":913112,"uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"<em>而在滿清滅亡之後，皇族很多改姓金。</em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9Na6WZ2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9Na6WZ2.jpg&h=d9bbc524&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5ad017a49f5b864bf4a253031d1a645193abffd2","tid":913112,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:52:40.000Z","msg":"宋徽宗俾人捉撚去做種馬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4f74c243fcce818fbce75df778c307a88b9079","tid":913112,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"總之全撚部都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1486af7f39dc5620fcfea784fcfb8af92f20a094","tid":913112,"uid":100638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc4f74c243fcce818fbce75df778c307a88b9079","tid":913112,"uid":31389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T08:53:51.000Z","msg":"總之全撚部都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T09:03:39.000Z","msg":"所以姐係中國人好鐘意打返自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.